Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.91,0:00:19.29,Default,,0,0,0,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.08,0:00:30.91,Default,,0,0,0,,How interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.91,0:00:32.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Grandfather?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.74,0:00:37.62,Default,,0,0,0,,That last psychokinetic blast\Ncame from the 3H, didn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.62,0:00:43.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I've never heard of anyone developing\Nrobots that could use psychic powers.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.45,0:00:48.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Neither have I... I don't believe\Nit's possible for current technology.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.66,0:00:52.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I shouldn't think so.\NWhich would mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.66,0:00:58.95,Default,,0,0,0,,a nonmachine element resides in that 3H.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.95,0:01:02.62,Default,,0,0,0,,So, the demon has inhabited\Nthe robot, has it?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.62,0:01:08.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I've received reports about the parasites,\Nbut I didn't hear anything about this.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.24,0:01:11.45,Default,,0,0,0,,We haven't received reports of it, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.45,0:01:14.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I've only heard about it\Nthrough personal conversations.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.12,0:01:16.24,Default,,0,0,0,,No, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.24,0:01:19.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I wasn't criticizing you, Kyouko.\NI was just thinking about...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.74,0:01:22.41,Default,,0,0,0,,how fascinating it was.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.45,0:01:29.16,Default,,0,0,0,,To think that you could use\Na humanoid robot this way...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.62,0:03:09.37,Default,,0,0,0,,This isn't good, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.37,0:03:13.29,Default,,0,0,0,,That psychic display\Nmust've been seen.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.29,0:03:16.24,Default,,0,0,0,,The police will be upon us presently.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.24,0:03:19.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Brother, should we leave here\Nfor the time being?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.33,0:03:20.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.74,0:03:22.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Tatsuya!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.54,0:03:24.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry! We're late!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.79,0:03:27.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Good timing.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.45,0:03:29.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Leo, you came, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.58,0:03:34.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. I got them to let me tag along.\NPartly for rehab.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.24,0:03:35.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, don't overdo it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.58,0:03:36.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.79,0:03:38.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Erika...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.24,0:03:39.62,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.62,0:03:42.91,Default,,0,0,0,,We need to leave this place\Nas quickly as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.91,0:03:46.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you prepare a way\Nto carry the three of them?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.16,0:03:49.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Um... We can take them to the storehouse\Nat Miki's place. Is that okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.87,0:03:52.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that okay, Mikihiko?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.24,0:03:53.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.62,0:03:58.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, that was our job\Nas Ancient Magic users to begin with.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.29,0:04:02.30,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, then me, Miki,\Nand I guess Leo, will take over here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.30,0:04:02.70,Default,,0,0,0,,You guess?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.70,0:04:05.41,Default,,0,0,0,,You three should go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.41,0:04:08.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, why?\NWe'll wait for you to load up.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.95,0:04:12.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Tatsuya, well, that is...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.62,0:04:21.95,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll take a cabinet.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.95,0:04:23.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I think that would be best.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.04,0:04:36.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Brother, whatever might you\Nbe worried about?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.99,0:04:39.87,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not that I'm worried, really, it's just...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.87,0:04:45.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Honoka, when Pixie released\Nthat powerful psychokinetic blast earlier...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.37,0:04:48.20,Default,,0,0,0,,did you get a sense of what happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.20,0:04:51.54,Default,,0,0,0,,No, why? What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.54,0:04:54.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd like you to listen calmly.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.24,0:04:56.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Just before Pixie fired the psychic blast,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.70,0:05:00.24,Default,,0,0,0,,she'd been supplied\Nwith Psions from you, Honoka.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.45,0:05:07.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you mean to say\Nthat Honoka provided Pixie with strength?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.41,0:05:10.87,Default,,0,0,0,,No, it didn't exactly seem like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.87,0:05:12.91,Default,,0,0,0,,It was similar to the process
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.91,0:05:17.45,Default,,0,0,0,,of injecting Psions into a CAD\Nwhen you want to expand an activation sequence.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.45,0:05:21.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Something like priming.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.04,0:05:24.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Or maybe resonance.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.20,0:05:28.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Mizuki said something\Nlike the parasite copied Honoka's thoughts.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.79,0:05:33.79,Default,,0,0,0,,There really seems to be\Nsome sort of path between Honoka and Pixie.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.79,0:05:36.29,Default,,0,0,0,,And it seems like...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.74,0:05:45.70,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems like the medium for it\Nis your hair ornaments, Honoka.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.04,0:05:49.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Specifically, those crystals.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.87,0:05:54.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't have any idea\Nwhat sort of logic is at work here, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.74,0:06:13.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Tatsuya gave me\Nthese precious hair ornaments!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.37,0:06:15.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want to lose them!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.91,0:06:20.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Setting aside the operative\Nprinciples for now...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.45,0:06:23.24,Default,,0,0,0,,we'll have to find a way to control it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.04,0:06:33.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, how are we going to carry these guys?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.08,0:06:36.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll call a car. That'll work, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.33,0:06:38.91,Default,,0,0,0,,You there, what are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.62,0:06:49.24,Default,,0,0,0,,You're all in high school, aren't you?\NWhat are you doing here at this hour?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.24,0:06:51.41,Default,,0,0,0,,What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.41,0:06:53.66,Default,,0,0,0,,What the hell were you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.66,0:06:56.62,Default,,0,0,0,,No, well, you see--
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.62,0:06:59.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I should be asking you. Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.29,0:07:00.27,Default,,0,0,0,,What was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.27,0:07:01.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Erika...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.66,0:07:06.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Didn't you hear me?\NI asked your names and rank.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.20,0:07:07.54,Default,,0,0,0,,What, you don't know?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.54,0:07:10.33,Default,,0,0,0,,There aren't any policemen\Nin this area right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.33,0:07:12.83,Default,,0,0,0,,They were ordered to leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.83,0:07:16.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Even that stupid brother of mine\Nwouldn't cut corners at a time like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.41,0:07:18.29,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you jabbering about?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.29,0:07:21.54,Default,,0,0,0,,You should've pretended to be detectives\Nin civilian clothing to better disguise yourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.54,0:07:24.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, I would've at least heard you out.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.12,0:07:27.54,Default,,0,0,0,,You know you can't get out of this\Nwith that nonsense!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.54,0:07:30.62,Default,,0,0,0,,We've caught you committing\Na violent crime! You're coming with us!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.62,0:07:34.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Really? You're still\Ngoing to play the fool, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.08,0:07:36.20,Default,,0,0,0,,That's too bad for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.20,0:07:40.70,Default,,0,0,0,,We stopped these three\Nduring an attempted sexual assault.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.70,0:07:44.95,Default,,0,0,0,,And we were just waiting\Nfor actual police officers to get here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.95,0:07:49.91,Default,,0,0,0,,This is no place for imitations.\NAm I making myself clear here?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.91,0:07:52.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm impressed how she can spin a story\Noff the top of her head.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.95,0:07:54.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Mikihiko!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.62,0:08:05.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Leo, get back!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.83,0:08:20.04,Default,,0,0,0,,They make those?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.04,0:08:45.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Thunder Child!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.04,0:08:50.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are Leo and Erika?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.79,0:09:18.49,Default,,0,0,0,,We're being pulled away\Nfrom the parasites.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.49,0:09:23.79,Default,,0,0,0,,We have to finish this quickly\Neven if it means being somewhat forceful.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.79,0:09:25.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Get down!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.41,0:09:53.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll get 'em!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.74,0:09:56.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't, Erika!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.33,0:09:59.83,Default,,0,0,0,,If you shot them out of the sky here,\Nit would cause a massive tragedy.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.04,0:10:04.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, that throws a wrench into things.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.99,0:10:09.29,Default,,0,0,0,,A call is coming in from the stealth team.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.29,0:10:11.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Open the line.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.24,0:10:15.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Reporting in. The mission was a success.\NSample secured.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.99,0:10:20.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Despite the accident,\Nyou seem to have accomplished your objective.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.74,0:10:23.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Bring them into the ice box as planned.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.37,0:10:26.29,Default,,0,0,0,,And go heavy on the drugs just in case.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.29,0:10:27.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir!
