Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.08,0:10:39.99,Default,,0,0,0,,You had something to talk about?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.33,0:10:45.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Tatsuya, well, actually...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.29,0:10:48.87,Default,,0,0,0,,What, did you let the parasites\Nget away or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.08,0:10:54.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not going to get mad\Nat something like that, so stop worrying.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.37,0:10:56.70,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't do anything about them\Nnow that they got away.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.70,0:10:58.58,Default,,0,0,0,,No, that's not it, Tatsuya!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.58,0:11:02.04,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right! They didn't escape!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.04,0:11:06.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I mean, I guess they did, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.04,0:11:10.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Someone swooped in and grabbed 'em.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.74,0:11:13.45,Default,,0,0,0,,They were that strong?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.45,0:11:16.04,Default,,0,0,0,,It may sound like we're being sore losers,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.04,0:11:19.41,Default,,0,0,0,,but I don't think they were really that strong\Nin terms of their abilities.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.41,0:11:19.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.90,0:11:22.33,Default,,0,0,0,,But they came fully armed.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.33,0:11:25.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I've never seen a suit that shocked you\Nwhenever you punched it before.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.70,0:11:28.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Every time I hit it,\Nthis powder sprayed everywhere!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.87,0:11:33.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I should've brought a weapon\Nwith more reach!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.62,0:11:34.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.99,0:11:38.79,Default,,0,0,0,,And then the parasites got taken away\Non a black airship.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.79,0:11:40.79,Default,,0,0,0,,It makes me so mad!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.79,0:11:44.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I'm glad nothing worse happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.12,0:11:47.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Tatsuya, you know who they were?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.12,0:11:48.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.33,0:11:54.16,Default,,0,0,0,,If they used such interesting gear\Nand a stealth-equipped airship...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.16,0:11:58.91,Default,,0,0,0,,it has to be the Japan Ground Defense Force's\Ncounterintelligence Section Three.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.91,0:12:03.70,Default,,0,0,0,,If we know who we're up against, don't we\Nknow where they brought the parasites to?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.70,0:12:06.62,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't narrow it down\Nif we don't know what they're after.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.95,0:12:09.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.74,0:12:13.95,Default,,0,0,0,,They're a government agency, so they can\Nprobably have as many bases as they need.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.95,0:12:16.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, they've got a budget.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.54,0:12:18.87,Default,,0,0,0,,They can't just have a hundred.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.87,0:12:24.66,Default,,0,0,0,,But they're probably hidden all over the place,\Nso well even a thorough search wouldn't work.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.66,0:12:27.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, we don't have to worry about it much.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.87,0:12:33.45,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll just have to make sure nobody\Ncan barge in this time. We'll set a trap.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.37,0:12:42.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning, Ms. Balance.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.37,0:12:45.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I apologize for calling so early, Colonel.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.41,0:12:49.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, it's you. Did you have\Nsomething to tell me?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.41,0:12:50.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.62,0:12:57.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Yesterday, the JGDF counterintelligence\Ndepartment's Section Three captured parasites.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.70,0:13:03.83,Default,,0,0,0,,We discovered one of them is a magician\Nformerly belonging to the USNA military.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.83,0:13:06.87,Default,,0,0,0,,The parasites have begun moving again?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.87,0:13:12.66,Default,,0,0,0,,It's possible that after the parasites' vessels\Nwere destroyed, they found new hosts.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.66,0:13:15.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Here are the ones\Nthat have been captured.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.99,0:13:20.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Three parasites have now\Nbeen taken prisoner.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.08,0:13:24.74,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the only one we've identified\Nthus far, but if you wish...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.74,0:13:29.12,Default,,0,0,0,,we can tell you where they are being held.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.12,0:13:32.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Please do, Ms. Kuroba.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.04,0:13:33.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.95,0:13:48.62,Default,,0,0,0,,That's about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.62,0:13:52.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I believe that airship belonged to the information\Nbureau's counterintelligence Section Three,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.29,0:13:56.12,Default,,0,0,0,,rumored to have ties to the Saegusa Family.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.12,0:14:00.45,Default,,0,0,0,,If you're considering using the parasites\Nfor military purposes, that would be dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.45,0:14:03.37,Default,,0,0,0,,We don't know for sure\Nhow to destroy them...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.37,0:14:06.29,Default,,0,0,0,,so I think we should be sealing them.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.29,0:14:08.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Counterintelligence Section Three?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.66,0:14:11.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Even I didn't know that,\Ndespite being a member of the Saegusa family,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.16,0:14:13.87,Default,,0,0,0,,so I'm surprised you know about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.87,0:14:18.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd appreciate it if you didn't ask\Nwhat my information source is.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.62,0:14:23.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, you probably have a lot\Nof your own things going on, so I won't.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.08,0:14:24.49,Default,,0,0,0,,More importantly...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.49,0:14:28.33,Default,,0,0,0,,why didn't you tell me\Nyou were going out to capture the parasites?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.33,0:14:33.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Because I figured bringing more people\Nalong would make them cautious.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.24,0:14:39.62,Default,,0,0,0,,It does make sense, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.62,0:14:45.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, you want me to explain\Nthis to my father, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.83,0:14:50.24,Default,,0,0,0,,And get the information bureau to give back the\Nparasites they snatched to Erika and the others?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.24,0:14:53.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't tell you to get them\Nto give them back...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.12,0:14:56.41,Default,,0,0,0,,but once you've verified the reason\Nthey took the parasites away,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.41,0:14:58.70,Default,,0,0,0,,if they're trying to deal with them\Nin any other way than sealing them,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.70,0:15:01.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd like you to warn them off.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.45,0:15:03.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell them that if the public finds out
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.04,0:15:05.08,Default,,0,0,0,,that the information bureau is\Ntaking advantage of the parasites
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.08,0:15:08.66,Default,,0,0,0,,and magicians face\Ndisadvantages because of it,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.66,0:15:12.20,Default,,0,0,0,,they'll be the ones\Npaying for the damages.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.41,0:15:15.49,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a scary thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.49,0:15:21.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Considering what's happening in the USNA,\NI believe the threat is necessary.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.66,0:15:26.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Will do.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.16,0:15:27.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll talk to my father.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.99,0:15:32.83,Default,,0,0,0,,But I can't promise any results,\Nso don't expect too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.83,0:15:38.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Unlike Jumonji, I don't have\Nfree reign over the Saegusa.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.41,0:15:40.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.91,0:15:43.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,500)\shad2\fs39\bord0\fnOpen Sans Light\b0\3c&H000000&\u1\pos(288,90)\c&HFFFFFF&\4c&H000000&\clip(128,46,328,126)\t(0,50,\clip(128,46,440,130))}FEBRUARY 18, 2096
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.08,0:15:50.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Saegusa...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.30,0:15:56.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an1\bord0\c&HD8CEBA&\move(664,169,661,136)}MAYUMI SAEGUSA
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.30,0:15:56.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an1\bord0\c&HD8CEBA&\move(664,281,663.111,248)}CONFIRMATION
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.30,0:15:56.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an7\bord0\c&HADA17B&\fnOpen Sans\move(248,571,248,540)}A spy holding facility belonging to\Ncounterintelligence Section Three has been\Nattacked, and the captured parasites were killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.24,0:16:15.87,Default,,0,0,0,,This?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.83,0:16:32.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Lina...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.79,0:16:49.08,Default,,0,0,0,,They make her do cruel things.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.08,0:16:51.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Brother, was that...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.58,0:16:53.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Lina?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.79,0:16:54.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Probably.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.54,0:17:00.91,Default,,0,0,0,,A homicidal act, clearly without any thought\Ngiven to the contents within.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.91,0:17:04.79,Default,,0,0,0,,The goal was only to burn\Nthe containers to cinders.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.79,0:17:06.49,Default,,0,0,0,,It had been an execution.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.66,0:17:12.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Assassinations are lonely\Nand cheerless work.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.24,0:17:15.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Without a high degree of affinity\Npersonality-wise,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.08,0:17:18.04,Default,,0,0,0,,it's too heavy for a teenage girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.04,0:17:20.12,Default,,0,0,0,,So heavy she won't be able to endure.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.12,0:17:23.41,Default,,0,0,0,,It will crush her heart, little by little.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.41,0:17:25.49,Default,,0,0,0,,And Lina doesn't have...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.49,0:17:28.08,Default,,0,0,0,,the affinity to be an assassin.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.54,0:17:36.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello! Can you hear me?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.62,0:17:41.95,Default,,0,0,0,,It's okay, Miyuki. This room is free\Nof any sort of microphones or cameras.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.95,0:17:46.00,Default,,0,0,0,,He's just talking at us.\NWe can't communicate.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.45,0:17:47.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}I'm going to assume you can,\Nif that's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.45,0:17:49.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll start with an introduction.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.79,0:17:53.29,Default,,0,0,0,,My name is Raymond Sage Clark.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.29,0:17:55.79,Default,,0,0,0,,One of the Seven Sages.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.79,0:17:57.62,Default,,0,0,0,,The Seven Sages...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.33,0:18:02.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard about you from Tia... or rather...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.37,0:18:04.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Shizuku.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.54,0:18:06.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Pleased to meet you, Tatsuya!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.33,0:18:10.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I see. He's Shizuku's information source.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.37,0:18:12.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll cut to the chase.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.29,0:18:16.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm the one who told Angie Sirius\Nabout counterintelligence Section Three.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.99,0:18:22.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Although it seems like she somehow\Nlearned of this before I informed her.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.24,0:18:26.41,Default,,0,0,0,,And I also wanted to give you the scoop.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.41,0:18:30.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I think you'll find it highly beneficial.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.49,0:18:34.24,Default,,0,0,0,,The magician boycott movements\Nraging fiercely in the States right now,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.24,0:18:37.91,Default,,0,0,0,,the ones starting to gain traction in Japan,\Nwere set up by one of the Seven Sages.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.91,0:18:40.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Gide Sage Hague.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.45,0:18:41.95,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.95,0:18:45.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Gide Hague... Also known as Gu Jie...\NA stateless overseas Chinese person...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.58,0:18:49.79,Default,,0,0,0,,and supreme leader of the international\Nterrorist organization, Blanche...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.79,0:18:55.37,Default,,0,0,0,,He's the boss of Hajime Tsukasa, whom you caught,\Nthe leader of Blanche's Japanese branch.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.37,0:18:57.41,Default,,0,0,0,,And also a senior member\Nof Richard Sun's group,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.41,0:19:02.54,Default,,0,0,0,,the previous leader of the international\Ncrime syndicate, No-Head Dragon.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.54,0:19:07.95,Default,,0,0,0,,In No-Head Dragon, they called Gu Jie\N"the Black Elder" or "the Great Hague."
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.95,0:19:10.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, and just so you know,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.41,0:19:14.95,Default,,0,0,0,,just because he's one of the Seven Sages\Ndoesn't mean I'm in conspiracy with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.95,0:19:18.41,Default,,0,0,0,,"Seven Sages" isn't the name\Nof a single group.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.41,0:19:23.33,Default,,0,0,0,,It refers to the seven operators\Nwith access privileges to Hlidskjalf.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.33,0:19:25.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Hlidskjalf...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.41,0:19:28.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I've heard a rumor about it once.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.41,0:19:30.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Does it actually exist?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.70,0:19:34.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Hlidskjalf is one of the additional\Nexpansion systems for Echelon III,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.16,0:19:38.08,Default,,0,0,0,,the global monitoring system.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.08,0:19:41.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Since it uses a backdoor in Echelon III,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.08,0:19:46.45,Default,,0,0,0,,maybe calling it a hacking system\Nlurking within the system would be better.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.45,0:19:50.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, Hlidskjalf collects information\Nfrom throughout the world
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.49,0:19:54.83,Default,,0,0,0,,and gives information\Nalong with search matches to the operators.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.83,0:19:59.16,Default,,0,0,0,,The system itself decides\Nwho the operators will be,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.16,0:20:02.62,Default,,0,0,0,,and we haven't found any logic\Nto how it chooses people.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.62,0:20:05.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Ostensibly, it's completely random.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.29,0:20:06.58,Default,,0,0,0,,This is insane.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.58,0:20:12.04,Default,,0,0,0,,And using Hlidskjalf\Nis a risk to the operators, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.04,0:20:14.99,Default,,0,0,0,,The operator's search history is saved.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.99,0:20:19.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Search history records\Nare how I learned about Gide Hague.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.62,0:20:25.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, wouldn't Gide Hague now know\NRaymond Clark's identity, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.04,0:20:27.33,Default,,0,0,0,,When Blanche's Japanese branch went under...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.33,0:20:30.74,Default,,0,0,0,,and No-Head Dragon lost\Nits Japanese headquarters...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.74,0:20:34.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Hague lost all his ways\Nto influence Japan.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.83,0:20:38.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Hague was the one who set up\Nthe parasites to come to Japan, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.33,0:20:44.74,Default,,0,0,0,,His goal is to rebuild his spy base in Japan\Nby taking advantage of the chaos.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.74,0:20:51.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I've deciphered that his goal\Nis to destroy magic through social means.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.37,0:20:56.08,Default,,0,0,0,,If he can get rid of it, the Great Asian Alliance,\Nwhich is behind the curve when it comes to magic,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.08,0:20:59.45,Default,,0,0,0,,will immediately see its military might\Nimprove compared to Japan.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.45,0:21:02.49,Default,,0,0,0,,To reign over a world without magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.49,0:21:06.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I think that's what Hague\Nand the people behind him are after.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.62,0:21:11.79,Default,,0,0,0,,His logic has leaps in it,\Nbut as a whole, it makes sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.79,0:21:15.12,Default,,0,0,0,,And that isn't what I want.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.12,0:21:17.62,Default,,0,0,0,,You can laugh at me,\Nbecause this is going to seem romantic,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.62,0:21:21.87,Default,,0,0,0,,but I think magic is a way\Ntoward a reformation of humankind.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.33,0:21:29.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, I'd like to keep providing you\Nwith necessary information in the future.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.74,0:21:34.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Tatsuya Shiba, the Strategic-Class magician,\NShiva the Destroyer.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.24,0:21:36.66,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a terrible nickname.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.66,0:21:39.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, this all got a little long-winded.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.62,0:21:45.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Basically, I'm proposing\Nto help you get rid of the parasites.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.91,0:21:49.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Tomorrow night,\NFebruary nineteenth by you,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.99,0:21:55.99,Default,,0,0,0,,lure all active parasites to the outdoor\Ntraining area behind First High.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.99,0:21:59.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, I want you to annihilate them.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.79,0:22:04.95,Default,,0,0,0,,And I've already given Angie Sirius\Nthis information, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.95,0:22:09.33,Default,,0,0,0,,You can cooperate with her\Nor compete with her, whatever you prefer.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.95,0:22:23.41,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll be late unless we leave soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.54,0:23:52.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\bord3\fnOpen Sans Extrabold\b0\c&HFFFEFC&\3c&H1D3EDF&\pos(702,68)}VISITOR ARC X